name: Biolab India
overview:
Biolab (India) was incorporated in the year 2005. Since then, we have grown in stature and accomplished many milestones. Today we are counted amongst the leading importer, exporter and distributor of Skeleton Models, Human Joint Models, Maternity Models, Medical Posters, Anatomical Models and many more. The product range has always been tested for high level of quality and workmanship. These traits have helped us to create a formidable position in the industry.

Milestone: Over the past few years, Biolab has introduced several new products, expanded its operations to keep pace with evolving customer needs. Today Biolab is the market leader and established a reputation in the respective market due its high quality products, competitive rates and best services.

Trade Fairs/Exhibitions: Regular participation in trade fairs and exhibitions, coverage in TV channels namely Kairalee TV and Doordarshan has resulted into more of awareness and greater visibility for our products.

Our Quality Assurance: We have always excelled in quality parameters and have set a benchmark in the industry as per our quality standards. To further educate our people we constantly engage them on certain platforms where in they interact with industry stalwarts and sharpen their base. This not only helps them to work with finesse, at the same time create a healthy image in the mind of clients.

Our Team: Our professionals work with a very dedicated approach to achieve production excellence. The market experience and industrial knowledge of these professionals has enabled us to target the consumers in right manner and to earn maximum profit. They keep close vigil on even the minor changes taking place in industry and ensure that their plans are further planned accordingly.

Our Product Range: Skeleton Models, Human Joint Models, Maternity Models, Medical Posters, Anatomical Models and many more.
